title: [Vinyl Rip] The Firm - Serious Fun
description:
This record seems to be exceedingly rare (even for purchase). So out of the goodness of my heart (and my record deck/sound card setup) I have bought, lovingly ripped and edited it into 192kbps mp3s.

The record is in excellent condition so you should be hard-pressed to find any clicks/pops, etc.

Track Listing:

01 Star Trekkin'
02 Girls Got Feelings Too
03 Arthur Daley (E's Alright)
04 Snookered
05 Heavy Metal Robot
06 Start Wrekkin'
07 Superheroes
08 Strawberry Ice Cream, Jelly and Cake
09 Monster Rap
10 Cash In Hand
11 Summertime On 42nd Street
12 Pop Stars

Enjoy. Seed. Distribute
